{"id":316910,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-张雪忠律师撰文呼吁各界关注刘萍案进展/","date":"2013-10-08T01:18:55Z","modified":"2013-10-08T01:18:55Z","title":"维权网 | 张雪忠律师撰文呼吁各界关注刘萍案进展（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><span></span></span><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><span>（维权网信息员龚萍报道）今天</span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>日），华东政法大学教师、律师张雪忠博士公开向社会发出《强烈吁请大家关注刘萍案的进展》，从法律角度陈述了江西新余公安、检察院等相关执法部门在办理刘萍案的过程中的诸多违法事实。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>据张雪忠律师陈述，江西新余市渝水区法院将于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>11-14</span></span><span>日召开庭前会议。刘萍涉嫌罪名：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>、非法集会罪，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>、聚众扰乱公共场所秩序罪，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>、利用邪教组织破坏法律实施罪。在侦办指控这些罪名上，新余警方存在严重的违反执法程序，甚至有伪造案情，严重侵犯刘萍律师咨询权等等问题。江西新余刘萍、魏忠平、李思华等人的被抓时间在今年全国同类案中不是最早的，但却面临要最早开庭，这显示刘萍案已成为江西新余当局要争先为中国今年来制造的一系列“公民案”寻找突破口与树立风向标。所以，张律师吁请社会各界关注刘萍案进展。</span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div><span><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span>  </span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mqookN9q3uY/UlLBXoWBWqI/AAAAAAAApK8/r_H1RZKAync/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E9%9B%AA%E5%BF%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%88%98%E8%90%8D%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mqookN9q3uY/UlLBXoWBWqI/AAAAAAAApK8/r_H1RZKAync/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E9%9B%AA%E5%BF%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%88%98%E8%90%8D%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81.jpg\" /></a></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<div></p>\n<div><span></span> </div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></